what is test driven development ?
in test driven development, test drives the design of production code. you write test first, then write
minimum production code to compile, then fail the test since implementation is not present, then do
minimum to pass the test, refactor and then start over the cycle again

TDD CYCLE
=========
write test => compile => fail the test => implement => pass the test => refactor => write test again


